ntive Protocol. <br/>\nProvide native on-chain incentive for developers.<e>**</e></STRONG><br/>\nReleased on Dec 31, 2018</p> \n\n<p>Incentives are the driving force of blockchain evolution. Nebulas Incentive (NI) includes Developer Incentive Protocol (DIP) and Proof of Devotion (PoD).<br/>\nDIP provides a positive feedback loop for developers to create high-quality decentralized applications.<br/>\nDIP will reward high ranking developers based on our open source Nebulas Rank (NR) algorithm. Rewards will be distributed in the form of Nebulas coin (NAS).</p>\n\n<p>Learn more about <URL url=\"https://nebulas.io/nova.html\"><s>[</s>Nebulas NOVA<e>](https://nebulas.io/nova.html)</e></URL>.<br/>\n<URL url=\"https://nebulas.io/docs/NebulasMauvepaper.pdf\"><s>[</s>Mauvepaper - Developer Incentive Protocol<e>](https://nebulas.io/docs/NebulasMauvepaper.pdf)</e></URL></p>\n\n<p>You can discuss everything about DIP with this TAG. <br/>\nAnd you can ask questions about <URL url=\"https://community.nebulas.io/d/25-nebulas-testnet-developer-incentive-program-event-guide\"><s>[</s>Nebulas Testnet Developer Incentive Program<e>](https://community.nebulas.io/d/25-nebulas-testnet-developer-incentive-program-event-guide)</e></URL>.<br/>\n<STRONG><s>**</s>Test DIP &amp; Get rewards NOW!<e>**</e></STRONG></p>\n</r>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'162.158.79.200',0,1),(263,52,1,'2019-01-26 18:27:43',31,'comment','<r><p>Some people ask me this question, perhaps they can<FP char=\"\">\'</FP>t get information clearly.<br/>\nDIP rewards are distributed directly to developers according to their Nebulas Rank (NR).<br/>\nSo, if you:<br/>\n1 Develop a DApp (OK. you own a smart contract)<br/>\n2 NR &gt; 0 in one week</p>\n\n<p>The creator address of this smart contract will receive DIP awards next Monday.<br/>\n<STRONG><s>**</s>Yes, all developers. EVERYONE<e>**</e></STRONG></p>\n\n<p>The board will be on <URL url=\"https://explorer.nebulas.io\"><s>[</s>explorer.nebulas.io<e>](https://explorer.nebulas.io)<